modules.description: This module implements macaroon creation, manipulation, and verification with support for first-party and third-party caveats. It works with strings for cryptographic keys, caveats, and serialized macaroon data, producing and consuming base64-encoded representations. Concrete use cases include constructing delegated authorization tokens with embedded constraints, securely binding discharge tokens to primary macaroons, and validating complex access policies across distributed services.
